            <div xml:id="One-and-Twenty"> 
                <interpGrp type="poembox">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="free"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="sad"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="love"></interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <lg> 
                    <l>When I was one-and-twenty,</l>
                        <l>I heard a wise man say,</l> 
                    <l>"Give crowns and pounds and guineas</l>
                        <l>But not your heart away;</l>
                    <l>Give pearls away and rubies</l>
                        <l>But keep your fancy free."</l>
                    <l>But I was one-and-twenty,</l>
                        <l>No use to talk to me.</l>
                    <l></l>
                    <l>When I was one-and-twenty</l>
                        <l>I heard him say again,</l>
                    <l>"The heart out of the bosom</l>
                        <l>Was never given in vain;</l>
                    <l>'Tis paid with sighs a plenty</l>
                        <l>And sold for endless rue."</l>
                    <l>And I am two-and-twenty,</l>
                        <l>And oh, 'tis true, 'tis true.</l>
